"title": "5564: suffering, of Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5564",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ suffered on behalf of his people, showing both the reality of his human nature, and the extent of his love for humanity. Those sufferings reached their climax in the sufferings of Jesus Christ upon the cross, through which God chose to redeem the world.</p>\n<h2>The OT foretold Jesus Christ's suffering</h2>\n<h3>NT references to the OT Scriptures</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25-Luke24:26\">LUK 24:25–24:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46\">LUK 24:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:2-Acts17:3\">ACT 17:2–17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:22-Acts26:23\">ACT 26:22–26:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3\">1CO 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>Types and foreshadowings of Jesus Christ's suffering</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:2\">GEN 22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:8\">GEN 22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:13\">GEN 22:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:22-Exod12:23\">EXO 12:22–12:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:5\">1SA 19:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:11-2Sam16:12\">2SA 16:11–16:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:15\">1KI 21:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:12-Ps55:14\">PSA 55:12–55:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:4\">PSA 57:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:11-Heb13:12\">HEB 13:11–13:12</a></p>\n<h3>Prophetic statements of Jesus Christ's suffering</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:2\">PSA 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:7-Ps22:8\">PSA 22:7–22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:12-Ps22:18\">PSA 22:12–22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:21\">PSA 69:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3-Isa53:12\">ISA 53:3–53:12</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ himself foretold his suffering</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:12\">MAT 17:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:12\">MRK 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:18-Matt20:19\">MAT 20:18–20:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:33-Mark10:34\">MRK 10:33–10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31-Luke18:32\">LUK 18:31–18:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:31\">MRK 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:25\">LUK 17:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:13-Luke20:15\">LUK 20:13–20:15</a> <em>compare with Naboth (1Kings chapter 21)</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:15\">LUK 22:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a></p>\n<h2>Aspects in Jesus Christ's suffering</h2>\n<h3>The enmity of Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1-Matt4:3\">MAT 4:1–4:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1-Luke4:3\">LUK 4:1–4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:5\">MAT 4:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:9\">LUK 4:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:8\">MAT 4:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:5\">LUK 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:13\">MRK 1:13</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:23\">MAT 16:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:3\">LUK 22:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:27\">JHN 13:27</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:30\">JHN 14:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:4\">REV 12:4</a></p>\n<h3>The hatred of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:7\">JHN 7:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:10\">JHN 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:20\">JHN 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:18-John15:20\">JHN 15:18–15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:8\">1CO 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection by his own people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:11\">JHN 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:1\">ISA 53:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:41-Luke19:42\">LUK 19:41–19:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:20\">LUK 24:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:40\">JHN 18:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:36\">ACT 2:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:13\">ACT 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10\">ACT 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14-1Thess2:15\">1TH 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>The failure of his disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:50\">MRK 14:50</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:56\">MAT 26:56</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:22\">MAT 16:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:40\">MAT 26:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:74-Matt26:75\">MAT 26:74–26:75</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:34\">LUK 18:34</a></p>\n<h3>Betrayal by Judas</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:23\">MAT 26:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:18\">MRK 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:21\">LUK 22:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21\">JHN 13:21</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment of his Son for the sins of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:5-Isa53:6\">ISA 53:5–53:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10\">ISA 53:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:25–3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:10\">HEB 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">HEB 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's willing submission to suffering</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:42\">MAT 26:42</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7\">ISA 53:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:11\">ISA 53:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:46\">LUK 23:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:7-Heb5:8\">HEB 5:7–5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:23</a></p>",
